lead_paragraph: The rest of Barcelona's squad will have to do "a little bit more" to make up for the absence of five-times World Player of the Year Lionel Messi for the next three weeks, according to captain Andres Iniesta.

headline.print_headline: Soccer: Barca Must Do 'a Little Bit More' Without Messi
